T1  - Intensive Medical Nutrition Therapy Alone or with Added Metformin to Prevent Gestational Diabetes Mellitus among High-Risk Mexican Women: A Randomized Clinical Trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3390/nu14010062
A1  - Perichart-Perera, Otilia
A1  - Mier-Cabrera, Jennifer
A1  - Flores-Robles, Claudia Montserrat
