T1  - Pioglitazone Metformin Complex Improves Polycystic Ovary Syndrome Comorbid Psychological Distress via Inhibiting NLRP3 Inflammasome Activation: A Prospective Clinical Study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1155/2020/3050487
A1  - Guo, Qing-Jun
A1  - Shan, Jing
