T1  - Effects of metabolic abnormalities, hyperandrogenemia and clomiphene on liver function parameters among Chinese women with polycystic ovary syndrome: results from a randomized controlled trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s40618-018-0953-6
A1  - Cai, W-Y
A1  - Gao, J-S
A1  - Luo, X
A1  - Ma, H-L
A1  - Ge, H
