T1  - The effects of fish oil on gene expression in patients with polycystic ovary syndrome.
T3  - Expression of Concern in: Eur J Clin Invest. 2024 Aug 25:e14306. doi: 10.1111/eci.14306 PMID: 39183383 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/39183383]
