T1  - The effects of metformin on simple obesity: a meta-analysis.
T3  - Comment in: Endocrine. 2019 Jul;65(1):219-220 PMID: 30689170 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/30689170] Comment in: Endocrine. 2019 Jul;65(1):221-222 PMID: 31168748 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31168748]
