T1  - Major depression, antidepressant use, and male and female fertility.
T3  - Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2018 May;109(5):797-798 PMID: 29778377 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29778377]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2018.01.029
A1  - Evans-Hoeker, Emily A
A1  - Eisenberg, Esther
A1  - Diamond, Michael P
A1  - Legro, Richard S
A1  - Alvero, Ruben
