T1  - Supplementation with omega-3 fatty acids and plasma adiponectin in women with polycystic ovary syndrome.
T2  - Suplementacion de acidos grasos omega-3 y adiponectina plasmatica en mujeres con sindrome de ovarios poliquisticos.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.endinu.2017.12.010
A1  - Mejia-Montilla, Jorly
A1  - Reyna-Villasmil, Eduardo
A1  - Dominguez-Brito, Lorena
